Requirements: 

     - MPS 3.0 (http://www.jetbrains.com/mps/download/)
     - Maven 
     - Ant
     - Ivy

1. Initialize git submodules

   git submodule init
   git submodule update

2. Compile the required modules and install locally

   mvn clean install

3. Setup workspace and resolve dependencies

   ant workspace

4. Launch MPS and open the project

5. Build the project with MPS

